== 杰利蝾螈 ==
弗吉尼亚是美国選區[[美國傑利蠑螈|劃分最不公正]]的州之一，无论是在国会层面还是在州层面，因为它的选区缺乏紧凑和相邻。
根据一项分析，2016年之前，弗吉尼亚州的国会选区在全国最差的选区中排名第五，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://strongernc.org/states-worst-congressional-gerrymandering-country/ |title=Which States Have the Worst Congressional Gerrymandering in the Country? |first=Brian |last=Kurilla |date=25 September 2017 |website=Stronger NC |access-date=2021-01-17 |archive-date=2021-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210702232418/https://strongernc.org/states-worst-congressional-gerrymandering-country/ }}</ref>因为县和市被分割成多个区域，从而形成了党派色彩浓厚的选区。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://onevirginia2021.org |title=One Virginia 2021 |author=<!--Not stated--> |website=onevirginia2021.org |publisher=[[OneVirginia2021|OneVirginia2021]] |access-date=October 13, 2020 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126213629/https://www.onevirginia2021.org/ }}</ref>

直到2017年被下令重劃後才有改善。

